## Social Media Optimization

### Open Graph Tags

The SEO component automatically generates OG tags:

```astro
<BaseLayout
  title="My Article"
  description="Article description"
  image="/images/og-image.jpg"
>
```

This creates:
- `og:title`
- `og:description`
- `og:image`
- `og:url`
- `og:type`

### Twitter Cards

Twitter Card tags are also generated automatically for better Twitter sharing.

